snippet.title: RETICLE_STAR - A Celeste-inspired platformer with single-screen levels!
snippet.description:
Download for free on itch.io https://nizakashii.itch.io/reticle-star?ac=qfCyYFQF-yt Get the key and step on the goal. If you get a star, you can use the dash. 

Try to clear all 70 stages!
